@startuml
title UC-44: View Tour Operation Logs

actor Guide
actor Admin
participant "GuideDashboardController" as GCtrl
participant "AdminOperationLogController" as ACtrl
participant "TourOperationLogDAO" as DAO
participant "DB" as DB
participant "guide/operation-logs.jsp" as GJSP
participant "admin/operation-logs.jsp" as AJSP

== Guide View (Timeline) ==
Guide -> GCtrl: GET ?action=operationLogs&scheduleId=X
GCtrl -> GCtrl: check session, role=Guide, verify assigned
GCtrl -> DAO: getLogsByScheduleId(scheduleId)
DAO -> DB: SELECT tol.*, u.FullName, r.RoleName\nFROM TourOperationLog tol\nLEFT JOIN [User] u, [Role] r\nWHERE ScheduleID=? ORDER BY CreatedAt DESC
DB --> DAO: List<TourOperationLog>
DAO --> GCtrl: logs
GCtrl -> GJSP: forward /views/guide/operation-logs.jsp
GJSP --> Guide: Timeline: vertical line + markers\nEach item: timestamp, activity, operator, role badge

== Admin View (Table + Pagination) ==
Admin -> ACtrl: GET /admin/operation-logs?search=&page=1
ACtrl -> ACtrl: check session, role Admin or Staff
ACtrl -> DAO: getAllLogsPaged(page, 15, search)
DAO -> DB: SELECT tol.*, t.TourName, ts.DepartureDate,\nu.FullName, r.RoleName\nJOIN TourSchedule, Tour\nLEFT JOIN [User], [Role]\nWHERE search LIKE?\nOFFSET 0 FETCH NEXT 15
DB --> DAO: List<TourOperationLog>
ACtrl -> DAO: getLogsCount(search)
DAO -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*)
DB --> DAO: total
ACtrl -> ACtrl: totalPages = ceil(total/15)
ACtrl -> AJSP: forward /admin/operation-logs.jsp
AJSP --> Admin: Search bar + Table\n(Mã Log, Tour, Hoạt Động, Người TH, Vai Trò, Thời Gian)\n+ Pagination
@enduml


@startuml
title UC-46: Moderate User Content

actor Admin
participant "moderation.jsp" as JSP
participant "AdminModerationController" as Ctrl
participant "ModerationDAO" as DAO
participant "DB" as DB

== View Content ==
Admin -> JSP: access /admin/moderation
JSP -> Ctrl: AJAX load tabs (reviews/posts/comments/history)
Ctrl -> Ctrl: hasModerationPermission()\nroleId==1 OR "Content Management"
Ctrl -> DAO: getPendingReviews / getPendingPosts / getPendingComments
DAO -> DB: SELECT ... WHERE IsVisible=1 (includes IsFlagged)
DB --> DAO: content list
DAO --> Ctrl: list
Ctrl -> JSP: JSON
JSP --> Admin: 4 tabs, each row: ID, content, author,\nstatus badge, flagged badge, action buttons

== Hide Content ==
Admin -> JSP: click "Ẩn"
JSP -> JSP: open reason modal (dropdown: Spam/Kích động/Sai lệch/Vi phạm/Khác)
Admin -> JSP: select reason → click "Ẩn nội dung"
JSP -> Ctrl: AJAX POST action=Hide, entityType, entityId, reason

Ctrl -> DAO: moderateContent(entityType, entityId, "Hide", reason, userId)
DAO -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
DAO -> DB: UPDATE {Table} SET IsVisible=0, IsFlagged=0
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ModerationRecord
DAO -> DB: COMMIT
DAO --> Ctrl: true
Ctrl -> JSP: {"status":"success"}
JSP -> JSP: reload tab

== Restore Content ==
Admin -> JSP: click "Khôi phục"
JSP -> Ctrl: AJAX POST action=Restore
Ctrl -> DAO: moderateContent(..., "Restore", "Khôi phục hiển thị", userId)
DAO -> DB: UPDATE {Table} SET IsVisible=1 + INSERT ModerationRecord
DAO --> Ctrl: true
Ctrl -> JSP: {"status":"success"}
JSP -> JSP: reload tab

== Dismiss Flag ==
Admin -> JSP: click "Bỏ qua" on flagged content
JSP -> Ctrl: AJAX POST action=DismissFlag, entityType, entityId
Ctrl -> DAO: dismissFlag(entityType, entityId)
DAO -> DB: UPDATE {Table} SET IsFlagged=0
DAO --> Ctrl: true
Ctrl -> JSP: {"status":"success"}
JSP -> JSP: reload tab
@enduml
